<h3 id="variation">Variation</h3>

<p>This species currently has no variation database. However you can process your own variants using the <a href="http://ensembl.gramene.org/Sorghum_bicolor/Tools/VEP">Variant Effect Predictor (VEP)</a> in Gramene. 
</p>

